id.description: The ID used to identify this component in Dash callbacks.

shapeList.description: shapeList is a list of shapes to be drawn on the image

zoomLevel.description: zoomLevel of the current OSD Viewer

curMousePosition.description: Current Mouse Position in Image Coordinates

viewPortBounds.description: viewportBounds of the current OSD Viewer

curShapeObject.description: curShapeObject is the current shape object that was most recently moused over

setProps.description:
Dash-assigned callback that should be called to report property changes
to Dash, to make them available for callbacks.
